data.description:
24" saturnia marble floors set on diagonal.  Large round marble display in front foyer. all very beautiful.  upgraded laundry room very nice.

Neighborhood Description

Very good neighborhood.  1 mile to state road 7 and 1 mile to Florida tpk.  2 miles to Wellington Green Mall.  New hospital.  New schools.  Much new shopping and many new restuarants.  We pay less taxes and still enjoy all the amenities of Wellington.
